                    h1 Day 1: MALL ROAD
                    h4 First and foremost is Mall Road that is the most famous marketplace in Murree. Here you will find all the unique items of Murree. The road opens till 3 am usually, people love to walk over there to enjoy the pleasant weather with yummy food items as well. 
