                    h4 Second, on the list of places must visit in Murree,  is Pindi Point almost 15 minutes’ walk from Mall Road. Tourists love to take a Chairlift ride that takes them down to 1.5 km from Pindi Point to Bansara Gali. Moreover, the scenery of the chairlift is a marvellous experience. 
