                    h1 Day 4: PATRIATA
                    h4 Becoming very famous with every single day, the new Murree as in Patriata approximately 15 kilometres away from the main Murree hills on the Lower Topa side. The hill station is newly constructed to cater for more of the visitor to the Murree. 
