                    h1 Day 6: RAWAT
                    h4 Rawat is another picturesque location in Murree district. Most notably, Mohra darogha, moori khambaal, sood gangal, dhok amban, and others. Additionally, Rawat district is very well known for having the facility of basic medical treatment.
