                    h1 Day 7: NATHIAGALI
                    h4 The Galliyat plays an important role in all Murree District and Nathiagali is the most visited Gali in Murree. For instance, Nathiagali is situated 35 kilometres from Murree and Abbottabad it is elevated at an altitude of 8400 ft.
