                    h1 Day 8: AYUBIA
                    h4 Next on the list is the Ayubia, it is the most visited spot after Nathiagali. It is the best picnic spot in Murree as it also possesses an Ayubia National Park which is elevated at 1,050 meters. Additionally, it is spread over 3,027 meters at the mountain tops within the valleys.
